dilbert is a simple command-line program intended to track tickets in a small it environment.

Requirements
============

0. A debian-like Linux (for our installation how-to)
1. A working Ruby environment (HEAD)
2. A working MongoDB.

Installation (most simple)
==========================

1. Install the required gems

$ gem install mongoid trollop

2. Download the deb package

$ wget https://github.com/pelgrim/dilbert/raw/debian/dilbert-tickets.deb

3. Install it

$ sudo dpkg -i dilbert-tickets.deb

Usage
=====

dilbert --help